OL,3,CNorthumbria Healthcare staff to walk
OL,4,Cout over 'missing wages', says union
OL,6,FHundreds of healthcare assistants
OL,7,Femployed at Northumbria Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust will be walking out
OL,9,Fin a dispute over wages they say
OL,10,Fthey're owed.
OL,12,FUNISON members will strike for 48
OL,13,Fhours beginning on Wednesday 16 July.
OL,15,FLast year, the union campaigned for
OL,16,Fthe trust to move the support staff
OL,17,Fonto a higher salary scale. Now,
OL,18,Fmembers say they have not been
OL,19,Fcompensated properly for the extra
OL,20,Fwork they undertook on the wrong pay
OL,21,Fgrade.
