OL,3,CNorthumbria Healthcare staff to walk
OL,4,Cout over 'missing wages', says union
OL,6,FThe trust, which runs sites such as
OL,7,FNorth Tyneside General Hospital and
OL,8,FAlnwick Infirmary, says it "acted
OL,9,Fquickly" to pay backpay to "those who
OL,10,Fwere entitled to it", and will "do
OL,11,Fwhat is required to ensure the safe
OL,12,Fcare of our patients".
OL,14,FHealthcare assistants had previously
OL,15,Fbeen on the lowest NHS wage band, but
OL,16,Fwere moved to a higher hourly wage in
OL,17,Facknowledgement of carrying out more
OL,18,Fcomplex tasks like taking blood,
OL,19,Fperforming electrocardiogram tests and
OL,20,Finserting cannulas.
