OL,3,CNorthumbria Healthcare staff to walk
OL,4,Cout over 'missing wages', says union
OL,6,FClare Williams, Northern regional
OL,7,Fsecretary for UNISON, said: "None of
OL,8,Fthe healthcare assistants want to go
OL,9,Fon strike. But the inability of senior
OL,10,Fmanagers at Northumbria to make them a
OL,11,Fserious offer has left them with
OL,12,Flittle other option.
OL,14,F"For years, staff worked way above
OL,15,Ftheir pay grade. It's only right that
OL,16,Fhaving moved them up the NHS salary
OL,17,Fscale, their managers give them a
OL,18,Fsensible amount of compensation to
OL,19,Fcover all the wages they were denied."
