OL,3,CNorthumbria Healthcare staff to walk
OL,4,Cout over 'missing wages', says union
OL,6,FThe trust confirmed the roles were
OL,7,Fmoved from Band 2 to Band 3 with
OL,8,Feffect from 1 April 2024, with pay
OL,9,Fbackdated to 1 April 2022.
OL,11,FA spokesperson from Northumbria
OL,12,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,13,F"We acted quickly to make the banding
OL,14,Fchanges and pay backpay to those who
OL,15,Fwere entitled to it.
OL,17,F"As always, we are committed to
OL,18,Fworking in partnership with our staff
OL,19,Fside colleagues on local matters, and
OL,20,Fwe will do what is required to ensure
OL,21,Fthe safe care of our patients."
